His fever’s almost gone.
Thank God.

40:18.166 --> 40:20.327
And Cam?
Are you kidding?

40:20.419 --> 40:22.250
She’s over the moon.

40:22.337 --> 40:24.919
The paramedics are here. She’s gonna
