41:36.411 --> 41:38.493
Dr. Brennan, I wanted to say thank you.

41:38.580 --> 41:40.741
Without your team,
I can’t imagine what would’ve happened.

41:40.832 --> 41:44.040
— Many deaths, I suppose.
- Yes.

41:44.127 --> 41:47.290
I hope, next time, we’ll meet
under less stressful circumstances.

41:47.381 --> 41:49.713
- I would enjoy that.
- Yeah.

41:49.800 --> 41:52.416
- Thorne’s in custody. You ready?
— Almost.

41:52.511 --> 41:54.342
You’re a lucky man, Agent Booth.

41:54.429 --> 41:55.965
Yes, I am.

41:56.056 --> 41:57.967
Very lucky.

41:58.058 --> 41:59.969
I think we’re all lucky after today.

42:02.562 --> 42:04.598
You ready?
Yes.

42:04.690 --> 42:08.729
You know that wasn’t real virus,
so I couldn’t have killed him.

42:08.819 --> 42:10.309
Figured.

42:10.404 --> 42:12.861
I would have used the real one
if I’d had it.

42:12.948 --> 42:14.688
Oh, I know.
[ Chuckles ]

42:14.783 --> 42:17.240
Because I would have missed Arastoo,

42:20.288 --> 42:22.700
Guy has no idea how lucky I really am.

42:22.791 --> 42:24.452
I mean really lucky.

42:24.543 --> 42:26.534
Aw. I love you too.

